"If your assignment includes a learner training step, the rubric must have at"
" least one criterion, and that criterion must have at least one option."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa kazi yako ina hatua ya mafunzo ya mwanafunzi, rubric lazima iwe na "
"angalau kigezo kimoja, na kigezo hicho lazima kiwe na chaguo angalau moja."

