msgstr "Kujifunza Kutathmini Majibu"

#: templates/legacy/student_training/student_training.html:61
msgid ""
"Before you begin to assess your peers' responses, you'll learn how to "
"complete peer assessments by reviewing responses that instructors have "
"already assessed. If you select the same options for the response that the "
"instructor selected, you'll move to the next step. If you don't select the "
"same options, you'll review the response and try again."
msgstr ""
"Kabla hujaanza kutathmini majibu ya wenzako, utajifunza jinsi ya kukamilisha"
" tathmini ya wenzako kwa kupitia majibu ambayo walimu tayari wameyathmini. "
"Ikiwa utachagua chaguo zile zile kama zilivyochaguliwa na mwalimu, "
"utaendelea kwenye hatua inayofuata. Ikiwa hutachagua chaguo zile zile, "
"utaangalia tena jibu na ujaribu upya tathmini."

#: templates/legacy/student_training/student_training.html:69
msgid ""
"Your assessment differs from the instructor's assessment of this response. "
"Review the response and consider why the instructor may have assessed it "
"differently. Then, try the assessment again."
msgstr ""
"Tathmini yako inatofautiana na tathmini ya mwalimu ya jibu hili. Angalia "
"jibu tena na fikiria kwa nini mwalimu anaweza kuwa ameyathmini kwa njia "
"tofauti. Kisha, jaribu tena tathmini."

#: templates/legacy/student_training/student_training.html:76
msgid "The response to the prompt above:"
msgstr "Jibu kwa ombi lililotangulia:"

#: templates/legacy/student_training/student_training.html:98
msgid "Selected Options Agree"
msgstr "Chaguo Lililochaguliwa Zinakubaliana"

